title: Zeit Gilgeous-Alexander 9/23: Collierville, Iron Dome, Tom Hanks, Jen Psaki, Tiger King, USB-C, Gersson Rosas
itunes:title: Zeit Gilgeous-Alexander 9/23: Collierville, Iron Dome, Tom Hanks, Jen Psaki, Tiger King, USB-C, Gersson Rosas
description:
In this edition of Zeit Gilgeous Alexander, Jack and Miles discuss the Collierville mass shooting, the House approving Israel's 'Iron Dome', which actors films to erase, Jen Psaki announcing border 'overseers' will be suspended, 'Tiger King' season 2?, the EU trying to get us all on the USB-C train, and Gersson Rosas being fired from the Timberwolves for being messy af
